node.text:
How cool is this 3D artwork by @shanef3d in Soho, New York? 🤯 Wanna see your pictures posted in our account? Apply for a feature on nomadfervor.com (link in my bio: @nomadfervor)

📽 @shanef3d
📍Zara Store in Soho, New York

This is Greece!🇬🇷 Get your photos posted in our account, apply for a feature visiting nomadfervor.com 👉🏼 the link is in our bio: @nomadfervor

Which spot is your favorite from 1 - 10?😍 Locations and Videos:
1. #Mykonos @momentsofgregory
2. #Meteora @shirley.films
3. #CavoTagooMykonos @juliagal_
4. #MykonosIsland @ftoon.ae
5. #AndronisLuxurySuites @juliagal_
6. #SantoriniSecrets @juliagal_
7. #MykonosTown @alexandradts
8. #Milos @katerinakatopis
9. #Santorini @momentsofgregory
10. #CavoTagooMykonos @takemyhearteverywhere

node.text:
Chased by a giraffe! 😳🦒We can post your photos in our account, follow the link in our bio: @nomadfervor and we will select your pictures

“This young male giraffe was orphaned at a young age and hand reared until he was able to survive in his own and be released back into to wild. So although this may look like an angry charge, it’s just the giraffe “keeping up with the herd” that he imprinted on as a youngster.

The giraffe chase happened unexpectedly and we did not force this moment. We do not encourage this type of interaction at all and in fact we avoid it at all costs so that the animal remains wild and free from human interaction. This was an unexpected and unavoidable moment.”

📽 @mattyardleyafrica
📍South Africa
